data.description: Step into this charming 3-bedroom 2 bath! Enjoy the cozy split floor plan & open concept living, but wait, there's more- a secret surprise, a community boat ramp for water adventures! Outside, relax under the covered patio & discover the raised garden beds, perfect for your green thumb dreams. Don't miss out on this home full of possibilities! Come and make it yours today!
